        "message": "Patch Set 10:\n\nMarcus, Steve, Seshu I was finally able to test this. Bellow is the behavior:\n\nIf Homing_Solution=oof OOF gets called\nIf Homing_Solution=$anything, SNIRO gets called\nIf Homing_Solution is not provided, we skip homing\n\nLet me know if this is correct.\n\nMarcus, for OOF to work using the java code, the propeties as mentioned in that patch are required: https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/71315/\nI don't know what those properties should be. If you tell me, I can update the patch, else feel free to hijack it.",
